UNTOUCHED asserts (this is itself the DoD-4 proof for the head). Kit
deploy now writes LANGUAGE="${ANSWER_LANGUAGE:-ru}" into profile.conf.
Log lines deliberately left operator-EN/RU (not owner-visible).

